        <div class="fr" style="border-color:#FFD60A;"><div class="fr-icon" style="background:#FFD60A55;color:#FFD60A;">🐳</div><div class="fr-text"><strong>Docker Alpine multi-stage:</strong> non-root UID 10014 · Node ≤16 for Windows Server 2012 compat</div></div>
        <div class="fr" style="border-color:#555;"><div class="fr-icon" style="background:#55555555;color:#999;">∞</div><div class="fr-text"><strong>Zero-state proxy:</strong> No sessions, no DB, no cred storage — pure stateless forwarding</div></div>
